        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1746036688
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes, despite their persistence in names, I'd encourage everyone to avoid using <code>succ</code> to mean plus one. Only use it when you are really talking about the inductive definition of Nat.</p>",
