        "sender_full_name": "Kim Morrison",
        "timestamp": 1746516600
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You mean use <code>add_one</code> instead of <code>succ</code> in the names of constants? Or avoid calling <code>.succ</code> in the code?</p>",
        "id": 516419564,
        "sender_full_name": "Martin Dvořák",
        "timestamp": 1746531252
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Why not both :)</p>",
